{
  "info": {
    "name": "ObatKu Pharmacy Management System API",
    "description": "Comprehensive API collection for ObatKu Pharmacy Management System\n\n## Features\n- Authentication & Authorization\n- User Management\n- Inventory Management (Coming Soon)\n- Transaction Management (Coming Soon)\n- Reporting (Coming Soon)\n\n## Setup Instructions\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set up environment variables:\n   - `base_url`: http://localhost:3001/api/v1\n   - `access_token`: (will be set after login)\n   - `refresh_token`: (will be set after login)\n3. Start with the Authentication folder\n4. Use the login request to get tokens\n5. Tokens will be automatically set in environment variables",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "obatku-api-collection",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3001/api/v1",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Base URL for the API"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT access token (set after login)"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT refresh token (set after login)"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-set tokens after successful login",
          "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
          "    const response = pm.response.json();",
          "    if (response.data && response.data.tokens) {",
          "        pm.environment.set('access_token', response.data.tokens.accessToken);",
          "        pm.environment.set('refresh_token', response.data.tokens.refreshToken);",
          "        console.log('Tokens set successfully');",
          "    }",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Auto-refresh token if 401 received",
          "if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
          "    const refreshToken = pm.environment.get('refresh_token');",
          "    if (refreshToken) {",
          "        console.log('Token expired, attempting refresh...');",
          "        // You can implement auto-refresh logic here",
          "    }",
          "}"
        ],
        "type": "text/javascript"
      }
    }
  ],
